  },
  {
    'text': 'Glioblastoma multiforme median survival is 15 months. Standard of care is maximal safe resection followed by concurrent temozolomide and radiotherapy then adjuvant temozolomide. MGMT promoter methylation predicts chemotherapy benefit.',
