  },
  {
    'text': 'Idiopathic pulmonary fibrosis with median survival of 3 to 5 years is slowed by nintedanib and pirfenidone reducing FVC decline rate. HRCT demonstrating a UIP pattern is sufficient for diagnosis without surgical biopsy in appropriate clinical context.',
    'title': 'IPF Antifibrotic Therapy Guidelines',
